 👩‍💻 About Me

I'm "Dipti", a cybersecurity-focused computer science student passionate about building **secure systems and real-world applications**.

From developing full-stack applications to exploring **penetration testing, malware analysis, and threat intelligence**, my work is driven by curiosity, security awareness, and continuous learning.

Currently focusing on:

• Building secure **MERN stack applications**
• Learning **penetration testing & ethical hacking**
• Practicing **Python for cybersecurity**
• Exploring **network security and vulnerability analysis**

I enjoy working on projects that combine **software development with security concepts**.


